Our big group tried this place last week and was pleasantly surprised by the quality of the food and service. I am a big fan of shabu shabu and have tried many places in ny and most did not have a flavorable soup base as this place. Most importantly the veggies / seafood were thoroughly cleaned and kept fresh. I ordered the regular soupbase w/ seafood platter and extra crab on the side. The crabs and scallop were meaty and fresh. I highly recommend this place as it is budget friendly and the food and service met my expectations. I
